sources.title: I'll See You in Hell (Crime, 1960) John Drew Barrymore, Eva Bartok | Full Movie
sources.description:
When thieves get greedy, trouble follows.
When a diamond heist goes wrong, the three would-be thieves go on the run from the law. After losing their partner in quicksand, tensions rise, and paranoia sets in. The arrival of a mysterious and beautiful drifter, Danielle, may cause even more trouble for them than the failed robbery itself.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/-5_Af0uuyjw

Original title: Ti aspetterò all’inferno (1960) AKA: I'll See You in Hell

This film is subtitled in many languages.

Director: Piero Regnoli
Writers: Arpad DeRiso, Dario Ferra, Piero Regnoli
Stars: Eva Bartok, John Drew Barrymore, Massimo Serato
Genres: Italian cinema, Crime, Drama, Thriller, Film-noir
